    "Refinement audits involve evaluating both the training data and algorithm performance which helps in detecting and mitigating biases that may be embedded within the data or the algorithms themselves (Abuyaman, 2023; Alkaissi & McFarlane, 2023; Anghelescu et al., 2023; Biswas et al., 2023; Zohouri et al., 2024).",
    "Collaborative research: Conducting collaborative research using GAI tools can make information more accessible and integrate diverse perspectives.",
